<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Cyber Security Services Request</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #f5f5f5; color: #333;">
  <div style="background-color: #fff; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 600px;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0;">Thank You for choosing Cyber Security Global LLC</h1>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Thank you for your interest in our cyber security services. We have received your request and will be in touch shortly to discuss how we can help protect your cloud infrastructure and data.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0;">Your Information</h2>
    <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;">
      <tr>
        <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; background-color: #f5f5f5;">Name</th>
        <td style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; background-color: #fff;">{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; background-color: #f5f5f5;">Email Address</th>
        <td style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; background-color: #fff;">{{email}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; background-color: #f5f5f5;">Phone Number</th>
        <td style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; background-color: #fff;">{{phone}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; background-color: #f5f5f5;">City</th>
        <td style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; background-color: #fff;">{{city}}</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <p style="margin-top: 24px;">If you have any questions or concerns about our services, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@cloudcybersecurity.com">contact@cloudcybersecurity.com</a>.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 24px;">Thank you,</p>
    <p>Cyber Security Global LLC Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>